summary: This is an FBI administrative document requesting the closure of the obstruction of justice case against Alfredo Rodriguez. It states that all investigative and prosecutorial issues have been resolved.

persons.name: Alfredo Rodriguez
persons.role: Subject of the obstruction of justice case
persons.context: He is the subject of the case (72-MM-113327) titled 'ALFREDO RODRIGUEZ; OBSTRUCTION OF JUSTICE' which is being recommended for administrative closure.

events.title: Request for Case Closure
events.description: An FBI agent drafts a request to administratively close the obstruction of justice case against Alfredo Rodriguez, stating all issues are resolved.

keyFacts: The FBI is requesting administrative closure of case 72-MM-113327 against Alfredo Rodriguez for obstruction of justice.
The document states that all investigative and prosecutorial issues in the case have been resolved.
The request was drafted on August 29, 2011, by the Miami Squad PB-2.
The case is identified as 'Pending' at the time of the request.
